title: Google\Cloud\Talent\V4\BatchDeleteJobsRequest
name: BatchDeleteJobsRequest
description:
Request to delete a batch of jobs.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.talent.v4.BatchDeleteJobsRequest

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.parent
params.description: Required. The resource name of the tenant under which the job is created. The format is "projects/{project_id}/tenants/{tenant_id}". For example, "projects/foo/tenants/bar". The parent of all of the jobs specified in names must match this field.

params.name: data.names
params.description: The names of the jobs to delete. The format is "projects/{project_id}/tenants/{tenant_id}/jobs/{job_id}". For example, "projects/foo/tenants/bar/jobs/baz". A maximum of 200 jobs can be deleted in a batch.
